description:
Are you looking to improve 3d printing skills?

3d printing can be a nightmare if you do not have the proper skills. In this course you will learn how to make 3d printing a walk in the park.


Well you have come to the right place!

In this course you will learn to;

1. Get Prints to Stick

2. Fine Tune Your Settings

3. Print Upgrades

4. Tips and Tricks

Plus a live 3d printing demo

I will walk you through the steps to set up a great print


FAQ

Q: Do I need basic 3d printing skills?

A: This is not a beginners course. You should know the basics on operating a 3d printer.


Q: Why should I take this course?

A: By taking this course you will greatly improve your 3d printing skills.


Q: Do I need a certain type of printer to make use of this course?

A: Any FFF or FDM desktop 3d printer can be used (Uses Filament). I will not cover other printing technology.
title: Advanced 3d printing Techniques
